6ad20cc9-8a7a-4fd8-99c6-7c7f88ec655e.title: Expanded Level 5 Driver's Seat
6ad20cc9-8a7a-4fd8-99c6-7c7f88ec655e.description:
Same as the Level 5 Driver's Seat, but it has 3 usable hotbars.
You can assign switches/buttons to the hotbars by colouring them accordingly:
-#ffffffWhite#919191: 1st hotbar
-#7f7f7fLight Grey#919191: 2nd hotbar
-#4a4a4aDark Grey#919191: 3rd hotbar
